{"type": "article", "id": 29720, "title": "用塑料做耗材的3D打印笔", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-18T11:55:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607172208544RJHxuBGrSDkoQch.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>是什么让你对 3D 打印笔望而却步？在设计师 Daniel Edwards 眼中，市面上的塑料线材定价过高，同时却有大量的塑料垃圾被白白浪费。为了让 3D 打印更亲民且环保，他设计了一款名为 Renegade 的 3D 打印笔以及制作塑料线材的切割装置 ChupaCut。Renegade 配备了电机和齿轮箱来传送材料，可以很轻松地将塑料或者其他常规的 3D 打印线材送进笔中进行加热。挤出的速度也可以通过触摸键调整，让作画更加顺畅。变废为宝的任务则交给 ChupaCut 来完成：利用内部锋利的刀片，它能够将整个塑料瓶裁成 3 到 12 毫米不等的细丝。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/232361696/renegade-the-first-3d-pen-to-run-on-plastic-bags-a\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，3D 打印笔的早鸟价为 60 英镑，塑料切割装置的早鸟价为 15 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160717220947OsBNUb7HK9qY4FSe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.573350\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607172209473DKYl9rFm2cjMQbf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160717220947rqgipFDaHtkPGKX4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016071722094790PemYDtJ71QVBzF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.553790\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}